{"home":{"description":"I'm a freelancer based in Edinburgh, active throughout Scotland and the UK. Working primarily in the camera department, I have experience as a camera trainee and 2nd AC on high-end projects and regularly work as Director of Photography and Colourist on short films and commercials. \n\nI have been involved in many different types of projects, ranging from feature films to live events. Currently, I also work as a director of photography at [MBP](https://mbpltd.com/), an award-winning Scottish production company.\n\nDespite a strong focus on cinematography and colour grading, I am also skilled in video editing, graphic design, and software development. This perhaps reveals what I enjoy most about content creation: mastering a wide array of technical skills to best articulate a creative idea.","metadescription":"Director of photography and colourist based in Edinburgh, and working throughout Scotland and the UK on a wide variety of projects, including short films, web series, music videos, or corporate videos.","metaimage":{"url":"/uploads/Untitled_a35be389d0.jpg"},"subtitle":"Cinematography • Colour grading • Software development","underconstruction":false,"images":[{"document":{"tags":[]},"image":{"url":"/uploads/betterfountain2_925bbf5860.jpg","width":1920,"height":1080},"caption":"Some of the statistics generated by [BetterFountain](/work/everything-else/betterfountain)."},{"document":{"tags":[{"name":"Short Narrative, Commercial","icon":"<svg version=\"1.1\" id=\"Layer_1\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" x=\"0px\" y=\"0px\" \t viewBox=\"0 0 11.5 13.5\" style=\"enable-background:new 0 0 11.5 13.5;\" xml:space=\"preserve\"> <path d=\"M11.5,9.5v-5L9,3.1V2.9l2-2L10.5,0L9,1.5l-2,2H0V10h3v3h1v-3h3l2,2l1.5,1.5l0.5-0.9l-2-2v0L11.5,9.5z M10.5,5.1v3.8L9,9.5 \tV4.2L10.5,5.1z M4,9V7.9c0.6-0.2,1-0.8,1-1.4C5,5.7,4.3,5,3.5,5S2,5.7,2,6.5c0,0.7,0.4,1.2,1,1.4V9H1V4.5h5V9H4z M3,6.5 \tC3,6.2,3.2,6,3.5,6S4,6.2,4,